messages.automaticMessage: Ixf ad itturjem s twurmant zɣ tspanyulit. Ur t isul iẓṛa bnadm. Iɣ trit at tawst ɣ tmuɣli, nermes aɣ s usiti dagi.
messages.originalMessage: Mad illan ɣ ixf ad ibedd f uḍṛiṣ amzwaru n tspanyulit.
messages.revisedMessage: Ixf ad iẓṛa t bnadm ittirjem zɣ uḍṛiṣ amzwaru n tspanyulit. Iɣ sul iḥtajja i uṣḥiḥ, nermes aɣ s usiti dagi.
